00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:34.100
I like the NBA and MLB.

00:07:34.100 --> 00:07:37.750
I could tell you all the
players names on every team,

00:07:37.750 --> 00:07:40.810
but I really have a hard
time making friends.

00:07:40.810 --> 00:07:43.850
The doctor said I would
never play team sports.

00:07:43.850 --> 00:07:47.710
&gt;&gt; Wrong. Never give up.

00:07:47.710 --> 00:07:50.710
&gt;&gt; The doctor said I
would never make friends.

00:07:50.710 --> 00:07:52.270
&gt;&gt; Wrong.

00:07:52.270 --> 00:07:53.570
&gt;&gt; You got to have hope.

